reviewText: Not what I thought it would be, but It was ok
It was good to watch one time as a movie, but I was hoping for it to be about electric cars, and it wasn't.

I received a copy of "WSTEC" as a gift. I thought it was very funny. I wound up renting it because a friend took my only copy. I only wish I could watch all the great behind-the-scenes footage that were on my DVD. Five stars!
This is a romantic comedy that my entire family enjoyed. Great story with believable characters . Well worth the rental.
